<plot>The author Jørn Riel tells the story about Mads Lange, the son of a Danish grocer from Langeland who travled to Bali in the 19th century and ended up almost becoming a king of the island. The documentary gives a beautiful portrait of the exotic Indonesian island. Jørn Riel follows the footsteps of Mads Lange.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?351413</url></doc>
